You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light.

Hannochs Smart Home products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light.

There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show.

After connecting Alexa to your Hannochs Smart Home products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our " Hannochs Smart Home " app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one account in our " Hannochs Smart Home " app;
(3). You need to have some Hannochs Smart Home devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our " Hannochs Smart Home" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "skill name" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "skill name" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "skill name", and you'll be navigated to Hannochs Smart Home login page;
(9). Input your Hannochs Smart Home account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
